('eaa6b901-adeb-4d01-a253-a22f61fbb3e2','ff6301bf-51f4-49a6-be06-e298ce1c8629','','','Casual day out','This outfit balances the 20°C clear weather with a light, breathable cotton base and a functional windbreaker for a quintessential streetwear aesthetic. The blue tones of the Bandit Europe windbreaker harmonize perfectly with the ''Crystal Blue'' accents of the Air Max 95s, while the black Rhude shorts provide a grounded, neutral anchor. The silver watch adds a subtle touch of hardware that complements the tech-focused textures of the outerwear and sneakers.','Wear the long-sleeve tee slightly tucked at the front of the shorts and leave the windbreaker unzipped to show off the layered textures.',false,'2026-02-17T06:58:46.472881+00:00'),
('828702d1-41db-41af-a991-ea2c4d409012','ff6301bf-51f4-49a6-be06-e298ce1c8629','','','Gym / Workout','This outfit embraces a high-end streetwear aesthetic perfect for the gym. The Rhude shorts provide a premium sporty vibe, while the Air Max 95s introduce a ''crystal blue'' accent that perfectly complements the Bandit Europe Windbreaker. At 20°C, the lightweight windbreaker is the ideal layer to handle the clear weather transitions before and after your workout.','Wear white mid-calf crew socks with the Rhude shorts to emphasize the streetwear aesthetic and bridge the gap between the shorts and sneakers.',false,'2026-02-17T06:59:14.322542+00:00'),
('08816616-4fe0-4695-93cc-3247195d41f6','ff6301bf-51f4-49a6-be06-e298ce1c8629','','','Date night','This outfit balances the ''streetwear'' aesthetic with a polished ''date night'' vibe by using a clean white base and well-fitting wide-leg trousers. The silver watch and Asics Gel-Nyc sneakers add a sophisticated, curated feel to the casual silhouettes, while the 21°C weather is perfectly handled by the breathable cotton long-sleeve. Darker tones on the bottom half provide a more evening-appropriate look compared to denim.','Push the sleeves of the long-sleeve shirt up slightly to showcase the silver watch and create a more relaxed, effortless silhouette.',false,'2026-02-19T06:09:05.065561+00:00'),
('b2f2a0e1-62ab-4030-ad05-d17c2360a0ae','ff6301bf-51f4-49a6-be06-e298ce1c8629','','','Night out / Party','This outfit embraces a Y2K-inspired streetwear aesthetic, perfect for a night out in 21°C weather. The light blue denim provides a classic base that contrasts beautifully with the crisp white long-sleeve, while the Air Max 95s bring in ''Crystal Blue'' accents that tie back to the jeans for a coordinated look. The silver watch adds a touch of metallic polish that elevates the casual pieces for a party setting.','Stack the hem of the jeans over the Air Max 95s to emphasize the chunky silhouette of the sneakers.',false,'2026-02-19T06:09:15.799937+00:00'),
('e33e7ee8-03d0-4b45-8668-11e6871f7c50','ff6301bf-51f4-49a6-be06-e298ce1c8629','','','Casual day out','This outfit embraces a Y2K-inspired streetwear aesthetic, perfect for 21°C weather. The light blue denim provides a classic base that contrasts beautifully with the crisp white long-sleeve, while the Air Max 95s pick up the blue tones from the jeans for a coordinated look. The silver watch adds a touch of metallic shine that complements the tech-runner vibes of the sneakers.','Push up the sleeves of the long-sleeve tee to your forearms to lean into the relaxed, casual streetwear vibe.',false,'2026-02-19T06:09:26.207873+00:00'),
('37d8d668-cdaa-427d-b533-c1009607f0bf','ff6301bf-51f4-49a6-be06-e298ce1c8629','','','Going supermarkey','For a supermarket run in 21°C weather, this outfit taps into an ''athletic-streetwear'' aesthetic. The grey wide-leg sweats provide a relaxed silhouette that pairs perfectly with the tech-focused Asics Gel-NYC, while the white long-sleeve offers a clean, breathable base layer. The dark grey zip-up adds a tonal layer for the air-conditioned aisles without being too heavy for the clear outdoor weather.','Leave the zip-up unfastened to showcase the clean white base layer and create vertical lines that elongate your frame.',false,'2026-02-19T06:09:45.81662+00:00'),
