('0ee2b332-5fbb-491d-a8e7-01de9ae1048a','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Brunch with friends','Navy knit crewneck, Nike sports top, Uniqlo wide leg joggers, and Cool grey jordan 4s work together for brunch with friends because the mix of jumpers, tops, bottoms, and shoes feels intentional from top to bottom. The navy, black, dark blue, navy, and grey, light grey, silver palette is balanced in a way that flatters your chestnut skin tone, giving you contrast and depth without making the outfit feel too loud for the occasion. The knit, polyester, cotton, and leather fabrics fit the tone of brunch with friends, balancing comfort with the right amount of structure and texture. It also aligns with your uk style preference, so the final look feels personal and believable instead of like a random mix of separate items.',NULL,false,'2026-04-17T11:45:42.476201+00:00'),
('fb0b7e0b-5691-4306-af74-454dfa0b9fd2','bbc090f6-51bc-4013-b878-0bd063d10ce3','','','Casual day out','This outfit is perfect for a casual day out, aligning with your streetwear and casual style preferences. The White "Open Your Mind" Graphic T-Shirt provides a clean and minimalist base, while the Washed Black Denim Jeans offer a comfortable, relaxed, and on-trend baggy fit. The Black and Grey Dunks complement the jeans, maintaining the casual and streetwear aesthetic. For your Light Beige skin tone, the predominantly white and black palette offers a sharp contrast that looks fresh and modern without overpowering your complexion.','For an extra touch of streetwear flair, try cuffing the jeans slightly above the ankle to showcase your Dunks.',false,'2026-04-18T03:41:56.050999+00:00'),
('fe00b638-8a9d-4279-8e29-b92b240b101c','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Casual day out','This outfit is perfect for a casual day out at 14°C, aligning with your UK streetwear style. The Black Nofs Hoodie provides warmth and a relaxed vibe, while the Washed Black Baggy Jeans offer a comfortable, on-trend silhouette. The Honey Black Corteiz 110s complete the streetwear aesthetic and the Orange Arc''teryx Alpha adds a vibrant pop of colour that flatters your Chestnut skin tone, while providing an extra layer for the cooler weather.','Layer the hoodie under the jacket for extra warmth and to show off the hoodie''s design.',false,'2026-04-20T07:04:11.127253+00:00'),
('6c46cdc2-21ac-4df3-b02e-fa08b246e676','b713753c-c455-4241-bfe7-2ca4ee54149c','','','Casual day out','This outfit is perfect for a casual day out, combining comfort with your streetwear preference. The Washed Black Wide-Leg Denim Jeans provide a relaxed, on-trend base, and the heavyweight denim is suitable for 12°C weather. Layering the Cream Standard Hoodie over a basic top (not provided but assumed) adds warmth and a clean aesthetic that flatters your Golden Beige skin tone. The Black Zip-up Hoodie brings in an additional layer for warmth and a touch of edgy streetwear style. Finally, the White and Teal Nike Dn Sneakers complete the look with their sporty-streetwear vibe and add a subtle pop of colour.','Wear the hoodie unzipped with a graphic tee underneath for an extra layer of style and personality.',false,'2026-04-20T20:07:53.044672+00:00'),
('2fc15069-dbe3-45e6-b533-7df1508a1661','ce39566e-4290-4461-9784-39fd2ee5a24a','','','Date night','This smart casual date night look blends your streetwear style with a touch of polish. The black Hoodrich Graphic Print T-Shirt provides a modern, edgy foundation that aligns with your preferred aesthetic. Paired with Dark Wash Denim Jeans, which are a classic and versatile choice, the outfit maintains a relaxed yet sophisticated feel. The P-6000 shoes, with their sporty-casual vibe, keep the comfort and streetwear elements prominent while still being appropriate for a date. Finally, the Silver Cuban Link Chain Necklace adds a bold and stylish accessory that complements your Warm Beige skin tone and completes the streetwear-inspired ensemble.','For a date night, ensure your denim is clean and free of excessive distressing for a polished finish.',false,'2026-04-22T08:38:25.644523+00:00'),
