('f2b9b15c-1a85-4976-bbec-739dd2180aa9','b713753c-c455-4241-bfe7-2ca4ee54149c','','','Brunch with friends','This Smart Casual brunch outfit leans into your streetwear preference while keeping you comfortable and stylish for the 13°C weather. The Washed Black Wide-Leg Denim Jeans provide a relaxed yet polished base, and their darker tone contrasts beautifully with your Golden Beige skin tone. The Cream Essentials Fear of God T-shirt adds a touch of on-trend branding and a light, flattering colour to your complexion. Finally, the White and Teal Nike Dn Sneakers complete the streetwear vibe with a comfortable and clean-lined finish, ensuring warmth while maintaining a smart casual aesthetic.','For an added layer of warmth and streetwear flair, consider throwing on an unbuttoned oversized flannel shirt over your t-shirt.',false,'2026-04-20T09:42:08.240888+00:00'),
('f034c3ba-1d32-49ce-869f-05f3fb1760b9','ce39566e-4290-4461-9784-39fd2ee5a24a','','','Casual day out','For a casual day out, we''re building a sporty streetwear look. The black Hoodrich Graphic Print T-Shirt provides a strong base and fits your preferred style, while the brown fleece sweatpants add an element of comfort and a complementary warm tone to your Warm Beige skin tone. The Light Pink and Grey Nike Air Max Sneakers tie the casual vibe together with a pop of muted colour. Finally, the Grey Cotton Beanie with Yellow Embroidery adds a street-ready accessory, playing into your sporty preference while also providing a subtle accent.','Roll up the cuffs of your sweatpants slightly to showcase your sneakers.',false,'2026-04-22T19:44:00.010582+00:00'),
