('3307d4d1-11c1-4f6b-bac1-67d185593a4f','ce39566e-4290-4461-9784-39fd2ee5a24a','','','Beach / Vacation','This outfit is perfect for a Beach/Holiday occasion, aligning perfectly with your sporty, casual, and streetwear style preference. The Cream Nike Logo T-shirt offers a light, breathable option for warm weather, and its creamy tone beautifully complements your Warm Beige skin tone. Paired with the Washed Black Denim Cargo Shorts, you get a relaxed yet stylish bottom that fits the streetwear aesthetic. The Light Pink and Grey Nike Air Max Sneakers, while not explicitly beach footwear, are perfect for vacation activities and provide a subtle pop of colour while keeping the overall look casual and sporty.','For a true beach vibe, consider swapping the sneakers for a pair of slides or sandals if you have them, and add the Armani Exchange Clear Frame Glasses for a cool and modern touch.',false,'2026-04-23T01:45:42.10471+00:00'),
('0678a681-853a-4671-b92a-40ce977025c2','ce39566e-4290-4461-9784-39fd2ee5a24a','','','Job interview','For your job interview, we''re building a clean, modern business casual look that still hints at your streetwear preference. The Dark Wash Denim Jeans in black are a versatile and polished base, fulfilling the smart trousers requirement while offering a refined edge. We''ll pair this with the crisp White Long-Sleeve Cotton T-Shirt, a foundational piece that elevates the denim and keeps you looking sharp. Completing the look, the Black P-6000 shoes provide a streamlined, contemporary touch that aligns with your sporty style without being overly casual for an interview. This palette of black and white is chic and professional, and while it doesn''t incorporate typical "Warm Beige" flattering colours, it offers a universally flattering, crisp contrast.','For a job interview that still reflects your personal style, ensure all items are immaculately clean and pressed.',false,'2026-04-23T01:45:58.292732+00:00'),
('ff28f7ab-7e3d-4e75-b3ff-0f82a9d82e75','ce39566e-4290-4461-9784-39fd2ee5a24a','','','Brunch with friends','This outfit is perfect for your "Brunch with friends" occasion, hitting the smart casual tier while embracing your sporty, casual, and streetwear style. The Cream Nike Logo T-shirt provides a clean base and pairs well with your Warm Beige skin tone. The Black Wide-Leg Denim Jeans with White Stitching offer a modern twist on classic denim, maintaining a relaxed yet polished feel. The Air Max 95 Gradients are comfortable and stylish sneakers that align perfectly with your streetwear preference. Finally, the Silver Cuban Link Chain Necklace adds a bold, on-trend accessory to complete this effortlessly cool look.','Consider a half-tuck of the Nike tee into the jeans to define your waist and elevate the casual silhouette.',false,'2026-04-23T01:46:19.408325+00:00'),
