('7076d6c6-43fc-4070-988f-d7d1c313aeb1','bbc090f6-51bc-4013-b878-0bd063d10ce3','','','Wedding guest','Navy and White Striped Cotton T-shirt, New Balance 550 White Sneakers, Black and Grey Dunks, and White "Open Your Mind" Graphic T-Shirt work together for wedding guest because the mix of tops, shoes, and bottoms feels intentional from top to bottom. The light grey, navy, white, white, and black palette is balanced in a way that flatters your light beige skin tone, giving you contrast and depth without making the outfit feel too loud for the occasion. The cotton, leather, suede, and denim fabrics fit the tone of wedding guest, balancing comfort with the right amount of structure and texture. It also aligns with your casual, streetwear, sporty, business-casual, vintage, minimalist, preppy style preference, so the final look feels personal and believable instead of like a random mix of separate items.','Consider investing in some formal wear staples like a well-fitting suit or a versatile dress to be prepared for formal events.',false,'2026-04-18T03:43:45.164848+00:00'),
