('b18c0822-089a-4d1a-a694-dc0d0e576743','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Casual day out','This outfit creates a cohesive and stylish casual look that aligns with your UK streetwear preference. The Gallery Dept. Washed Black Tee offers a relaxed, graphic element, while the washed black baggy jeans complement the streetwear aesthetic and create a balanced silhouette. The Honey Black Corteiz 110s tie the black and dark tones together, with a hint of yellow providing a subtle pop of color against your Chestnut skin tone, which beautifully handles bold and vibrant hues. This combination is perfect for a casual day out.','To complete the look, consider adding a simple chain necklace or a black beanie for extra detail.',false,'2026-04-23T02:14:29.929734+00:00'),
('4fe73a05-a064-4a5f-be79-098634e2054e','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Casual day out','This outfit is perfect for a casual day out, embracing your UK streetwear style. The Corteiz waffle knit Grindwear Dark Blue tee provides a comfortable and stylish top in a shade of navy that suits your Chestnut skin tone beautifully. Paired with the Light Wash Wide Leg Denim Jeans, it creates a relaxed silhouette that aligns with current UK fashion. The Honey Black Corteiz 110s in black and yellow complement the overall streetwear aesthetic and add a pop of colour without clashing. This combination achieves a cohesive, trendy, and comfortable look.','For an extra touch of cool, lightly cuff the bottom of your jeans to show off the sneakers.',false,'2026-04-23T02:32:44.275199+00:00'),
