('15538a9c-53ed-40ce-b75a-05ef978b4c93','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Casual day out','For a casual day out, we''re building a Neutral Anchor colour story around beige and black, which flatters your Chestnut skin tone. The Gallery Dept tee in beige offers a relaxed streetwear vibe that aligns with your UK preference. Paired with the Washed black baggy jeans, this creates a comfortable yet stylish silhouette. We’ll finish the look with the Honey Black Corteiz 110s, which lean into your streetwear preference while keeping the palette cohesive with their black and yellow accents.','To elevate this casual look, add a simple silver chain or a black baseball cap.',false,'2026-04-23T02:49:22.747191+00:00'),
('cded3e46-027d-49b0-8e0a-6a5d17386b4c','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Casual day out','This casual day out look centers on a neutral anchor colour story, combining shades of black, dark blue, and grey. The Gallery Dept. Washed Black Tee with its dark blue accents complements your Chestnut skin tone beautifully, while the Dark Blue Uniqlo wide leg joggers provide a comfortable and stylish base. Completing the outfit are the Cool Grey Jordan 4s, which pull in the grey tones and maintain the athletic street style you prefer. The relaxed fit of the tee and joggers keeps the outfit perfectly aligned with a casual, UK streetwear aesthetic.','Roll up the cuffs of your joggers slightly to showcase your Jordans.',false,'2026-04-23T02:49:31.317939+00:00'),
