('1b6fc4cd-3c22-4d13-8d25-991e3a274f72','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Casual day out','Black Nofs Hoodie, Washed black baggy jeans, and Honey Black Corteiz 110s work together for casual day out because the mix of jumpers, bottoms, and shoes feels intentional from top to bottom. The black, dark grey, black, charcoal, and black, yellow palette is balanced in a way that flatters your chestnut skin tone, giving you contrast and depth without making the outfit feel too loud for the occasion. The cotton, denim, and leather fabrics fit the tone of casual day out, balancing comfort with the right amount of structure and texture. It also aligns with your uk style preference, so the final look feels personal and believable instead of like a random mix of separate items.',NULL,false,'2026-04-23T08:03:05.672416+00:00'),
