('d84838ad-d56f-4d5a-a573-d1fa5212e760','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Casual day out','This outfit uses a complementary colour story, combining the blue of the raw denim jeans and the cobalt blue on the Corteiz Brazil tee with the warm yellow accents of the Honey Black Corteiz 110s. For your Chestnut skin tone, cobalt and yellow are incredibly flattering, making you glow. The chosen pieces reflect your UK streetwear preference with a relaxed, modern feel, perfect for a casual day out. The fitted polyester top balances the raw denim and streetwear sneakers, showcasing your athletic build without being overtly sporty.','Roll up the cuffs of the jeans slightly to highlight your sneakers.',false,'2026-04-23T08:03:20.489955+00:00'),
('248605c8-1640-457e-b5ee-84050fdced89','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Casual day out','For your casual day out, I’ve chosen a Neutral Anchor colour story to highlight your Chestnut skin tone, which truly pops against stark contrasts. The Black Chrome Hearts hockey shirt provides a comfortable yet stylish top that reflects your streetwear preference, while its mesh fabric adds a touch of athletic appeal perfect for a casual setting. Paired with the Washed black baggy jeans, this creates a relaxed, contemporary silhouette. Finishing the look with the Cool grey Jordan 4s injects a retro streetwear vibe, keeping the entire outfit cohesive and on-trend for a UK-style casual aesthetic.','Roll up the cuffs of your jeans to showcase the Jordan 4s, emphasizing the streetwear influence.',false,'2026-04-23T08:03:30.520645+00:00'),
('8b20497d-d806-43ae-b3b6-c63b09d7b4d6','0efc7833-4b0b-406a-9bc8-4ce683341c40','','','Date night','Black Hoodie, White and Olive Green Nike Sneakers, Navy Cotton T-shirt, and Black Pants with Embellishments work together for date night because the mix of jumpers, shoes, tops, and bottoms feels intentional from top to bottom. The black, white, and navy palette creates clean contrast and visual balance, which helps the outfit feel polished and easy to wear. The cotton, mesh, and polyester fabrics also make sense here, because they match the date night brief while responding well to clear weather at 12°C, which adds enough substance for cooler conditions without feeling bulky. It also aligns with your casual, business-casual, old-money style preference, so the final look feels personal and believable instead of like a random mix of separate items.',NULL,false,'2026-05-02T11:39:08.698043+00:00'),
('60400162-2a76-4f58-b759-6f4229c9bfad','0efc7833-4b0b-406a-9bc8-4ce683341c40','','','Casual day out','This outfit uses a Neutral Anchor colour story, combining classic black and white with a pop of silver. The navy cotton t-shirt is a comfortable and versatile base, perfectly suited for a casual day out in mild weather. The black pants with embellishments add a touch of modern style while adhering to your preference for neutrals and a slightly elevated casual aesthetic. The white and olive green Nike sneakers provide a clean and sporty finish, rotating away from recently worn shoes, and the silver watch adds a subtle touch of refinement that aligns with a "casual old-money" vibe without being overly formal.','For an effortlessly cool look, tuck the navy tee loosely into the embellished black pants.',false,'2026-05-02T13:33:59.49467+00:00'),
('f668e70a-37fc-4a99-9b02-e6c9a234ffd6','0efc7833-4b0b-406a-9bc8-4ce683341c40','','','Casual day out','For your casual day out, I''ve put together a cohesive outfit using a **Neutral Anchor** colour story with a pop of colour. The **Navy Blue Polo Shirt** is a classic choice, aligning with your business-casual and old-money preferences, while the tiger embroidery adds a subtle, personalized touch. Pairing it with the **Light Wash Wide Leg Denim Jeans** creates a relaxed yet polished silhouette that perfectly suits a casual outing in mild weather. The **Louis Vuitton Monogram Denim Sneakers** tie the entire look together, their denim matching the jeans and the blue perfectly complementing the navy polo. This outfit is comfortable, stylish, and embodies the refined casual aesthetic you appreciate.','For an extra touch of sophistication, consider tucking in the polo and adding a brown leather belt.',false,'2026-05-02T12:27:22.49358+00:00'),
('a504fb15-d51f-44ca-9923-4e7dcdc47b51','0efc7833-4b0b-406a-9bc8-4ce683341c40','','','Casual day out','For a casual day out in mild weather, we''re building a Neutral Anchor colour story using shades of grey with a pop of maroon. Your Light Wash Wide Leg Denim Jeans provide a relaxed, comfortable base that aligns with your casual style. On top, the Barkers Half-Zip Sweatshirt in Maroon adds a touch of richness and warmth without being too heavy for the 12°C temperature. Finally, the Louis Vuitton Monogram Denim Sneakers tie in with the denim of the jeans, offering a cohesive and stylish finish that aligns with your preference for luxury items. This outfit is perfect for your casual, old-money aesthetic.','Roll up the cuffs of the jeans slightly to showcase the sneakers and add a laid-back touch.',false,'2026-05-02T12:40:54.762651+00:00'),
('f41e9b4e-9e6d-4758-a1d3-ac5de63a9ac3','0efc7833-4b0b-406a-9bc8-4ce683341c40','','','Casual day out','This casual outfit is built around a "Neutral Anchor" colour story, using black and white as the base with a subtle pop of blue. The White Cotton Crew Neck T-Shirt offers a clean, minimalist foundation that aligns with your preferred neutral colours and minimalist aesthetic. Paired with the Black Pants with Embellishments, the outfit maintains a sophisticated yet relaxed feel, fitting perfectly for a casual day out while adhering to your style preference for elevated basics. The Louis Vuitton Monogram Denim Sneakers inject a subtle hint of luxury and a touch of blue, preventing the monochromatic base from feeling too stark. The denim of the sneakers complements the casual vibe while elevating the overall look.','For a slightly more dressed-up casual look, consider French-tucking the t-shirt to define your waistline.',false,'2026-05-02T13:50:40.893566+00:00'),
