('720299f9-3006-474a-aa0b-929be01e63e1','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Casual day out','This casual outfit for a day out uses a Neutral Anchor colour story, combining classic black, blue, and grey tones that flatter your Chestnut skin tone. The Gallery Dept. Washed Black Tee offers a relaxed, streetwear vibe with its interesting graphic, perfectly aligning with your UK style preference. Paired with the Light Wash Wide-Leg Denim Jeans, the outfit maintains comfort and a modern silhouette. The Cool Grey Jordan 4s tie the look together, adding a sporty streetwear touch while keeping the overall palette cohesive and ensuring comfort for a casual day out.','Roll up the hems of your jeans to highlight your sneakers.',false,'2026-04-23T18:35:57.439358+00:00'),
