('b757cd09-9eab-4b5a-a3f7-52c7f9a31db3','ce39566e-4290-4461-9784-39fd2ee5a24a','','','Going to watch a football game at night (cold) with mates','This outfit is built around a Neutral Anchor colour story, combining classic black and grey with a subtle hint of brown. Given the cold night and your sporty, streetwear preference, I''ve selected the "black as color hoddie" (21) for its warmth and relaxed fit, perfectly aligning with your style. Paired with the "Black Wide-Leg Denim Jeans with White Stitching" (34), this creates a comfortable yet stylish base for a football game. The "Air max 95 gradients" (35) offer both comfort and streetwear appeal, and the "Grey Cotton Beanie with Yellow Embroidery" (6) adds warmth and a touch of casual flair, making it ideal for a chilly evening with friends. The dark tones with grey accents will also be flattering for most skin tones.','Layer a subtle graphic tee under the hoodie for added interest if you get too warm.',false,'2026-04-24T07:25:30.102143+00:00'),
