('5874e828-39ba-4813-bdb8-2e4a6f52de3a','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','An outfit with a green shirt','This outfit uses a Neutral Anchor colour story, grounding the Forest Green of the Tommy Jeans T-Shirt with the Washed Black Baggy Jeans and picking up the subtle yellow detailing in the Honey Black Corteiz 110s. The casual cotton tee and baggy denim align perfectly with your "Street Formal" style preference, creating a relaxed yet intentional aesthetic. The sturdy denim and cotton are suitable for everyday casual wear. The Honey Black Corteiz 110s add a touch of sporty streetwear, staying true to your style and providing comfort. This combination offers a balanced look that is both stylish and comfortable.','To elevate this casual look, try cuffing the jeans and adding a statement watch or simple chain.',false,'2026-04-28T10:20:31.260297+00:00'),
('324e7097-7438-4a7e-bd28-6279bc701602','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','An outfit with a green shirt','This outfit works perfectly for your Street Formal style. We''re going with a Neutral Anchor colour story, using the bold Green Bay Packers NFL Jersey as the accent against the neutral tones. The jersey, made of breathable polyester, brings a sporty and bold element, which is balanced by the relaxed fit of the Light Wash Wide Leg Denim Jeans. To keep the casual, streetwear vibe strong and tie into the neutral base, the Honey Black Corteiz 110s are a perfect choice, offering both comfort and style. This combination creates a balanced look that is both striking and comfortable, ideal for everyday casual wear.','Roll up the hems of your jeans to show off the sneakers and create a more intentional silhouette.',false,'2026-04-28T10:20:38.022264+00:00'),
('9d1e6728-c454-4eb6-aae0-1807a1bc20ca','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','A business casual event','This "Street Formal" business casual look is built with a "Neutral Anchor" colour story using black, white, and grey. The clean lines of the Black Stone Island x Supreme Cotton Tee combined with the tailored Black Uniqlo Wide Smart Pants create a sophisticated yet modern foundation, fitting your preference for minimalist and monochrome styles. The sleek Black Prada Leather Loafers with Logo elevate the outfit to the "BUSINESS" occasion tier, ensuring appropriate formality while maintaining a touch of streetwear-inspired edge. This combination perfectly balances your "Street Formal" preference for a polished, contemporary aesthetic.','For an extra touch of street-formal style, consider rolling up the sleeves of the tee just once to expose your forearms.',false,'2026-04-28T10:20:52.679052+00:00'),
('ce24c7e4-a4dc-4660-9686-0a834d2a6c27','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Im going to an american football game','For an American football game, we''re going with a **Neutral Anchor** colour story to keep it sporty yet sophisticated, fitting your Street Formal style. We''ll start with the iconic Navy Dallas Cowboys NFL Jersey as your top, embracing the game-day spirit while maintaining a sleek, dark blue base. This pairs perfectly with the Dark Blue Uniqlo wide leg joggers, providing comfort and a relaxed, fashion-forward silhouette that aligns with your streetwear preference. To complete the look, the Cool Grey Jordan 4s add a touch of athletic cool and a neutral tone that ties the whole outfit together.','Layer a thin black long-sleeve tee underneath the jersey for added warmth if the weather is chilly.',false,'2026-04-28T10:21:11.647089+00:00'),
('a03e76e9-3715-455d-b954-4843c3e7aa30','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Im going on a flight','For your flight, I''ve put together a comfortable yet stylish Street Formal look using a Neutral Anchor colour scheme of grey and black, with a subtle pop of grey from the shoes. The Grey Broken Planet Zip-Up Hoodie in cotton offers warmth and a relaxed silhouette, perfect for travel. Paired with the Washed Black Baggy Jeans, also in cotton, the outfit maintains a cohesive streetwear aesthetic while providing ease of movement. The Cool Grey Jordan 4s complete this ensemble, bringing in a touch of athletic street style and ensuring all-day comfort for your journey.','Layer a base tee under your hoodie for versatility if the temperature changes during your flight.',false,'2026-04-28T10:21:31.597501+00:00'),
('067d887e-e804-497f-8b3e-67909a90eac3','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','A mainly grey fit','This outfit embraces a sophisticated monochromatic colour story with varying shades of grey, aligning perfectly with your "Street Formal" style. The Grey Cp Company zip-up offers a relaxed yet sharp silhouette, while the Nofs Grey joggers keep the bottom half cohesive and comfortable. Finishing the look, the cool grey Jordan 4s tie into the grey tones and add a touch of streetwear cool without being overtly sporty. This combination provides a clean, contemporary aesthetic perfect for a casual outing.','For an elevated streetwear look, layer a crisp white tee under the zip-up and add a simple silver chain.',false,'2026-04-28T10:22:29.423749+00:00'),
('256d083a-6237-4cf6-8cfe-1df6966e7396','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','An outfit to rob someone','This outfit has a "Neutral Anchor" colour story, using black as the anchor, with a subtle pop of yellow. The Black Corteiz Rtw tee, with its red detailing, pairs well with the Washed Black Baggy Jeans, creating a sleek base that aligns with your Street Formal style. The dark wash of the denim adds to the edgy aesthetic without being overtly casual. Finishing the look, the Honey Black Corteiz 110s bring in a touch of street style and a subtle athletic vibe, while the yellow accents complement the black without overwhelming the neutral base, achieving a balanced and modern feel.','For an extra edge, try a subtle chain necklace or a black leather bracelet.',false,'2026-04-28T10:22:44.28831+00:00'),
('8f2f5a68-4516-47d7-8e06-a7b71bab3a7b','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','An outfit with my raw denim jeans','This "Street Formal" outfit starts with the foundation of your raw denim jeans, grounding the look with a modern, structured base. I''ve chosen a neutral anchor colour story, combining the dark blue of the denim with the washed black and grey tones. The iconic Gallery Dept. Washed Black Tee adds a touch of streetwear cool with its vintage vibe and complements the raw denim perfectly in fabric and colour. Finishing the look with the Cool Grey Jordan 4s provides a clean, athletic contrast with the grey tones, creating a cohesive and stylish casual outfit that aligns with your "Street Formal" preference.','For an extra touch of sophistication, try a subtle cuff on the raw denim to show off the Jordan 4s.',false,'2026-04-29T05:24:01.191605+00:00'),
('24ce21d8-ceeb-4a19-8332-e2fb7907756e','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','An outfit with my raw denim jeans and a jumper','The chosen outfit embodies a "Street Formal" style, combining a sleek navy knit crewneck with raw denim jeans for a sophisticated yet relaxed aesthetic. The thin knit offers a clean line that works well with the athletic body type, while the rich navy in the jumper and the blue raw denim create a chic tonal colour story. Finishing this off, the Honey Black Corteiz 110s infuse a streetwear edge, perfectly aligning with the "Street Formal" preference and adding a touch of personality with the yellow accents against the black. This combination strikes a balance between tailored elements and casual comfort, ideal for a versatile casual occasion.','For an elevated touch, try a subtle cuff on the raw denim to showcase the Honey Black Corteiz 110s.',false,'2026-04-29T05:24:15.558945+00:00'),
('484a9f23-f6d3-4ba7-9340-18b50214e525','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','An outfit with my raw denim jeans and a jumper','This casual outfit anchors on the "Street Formal" aesthetic you prefer, blending comfortable elements with a refined edge. The raw denim jeans in blue provide a solid base, pairing well with the cobalt blue knit jumper for a sophisticated tonal colour story. The richness of the blue denim and the "Cobalt" blue of the jumper create a sense of depth. Completing the look, the "Honey Black Corteiz 110s" add a stylish, street-ready touch with their black and yellow accents, while keeping the overall palette grounded. This combination is clean and modern, perfect for an athletic body type and a neutral-loving aesthetic, especially given the cool undertones of blue.','Roll up the cuffs of your raw denim jeans once or twice to showcase the "Honey Black Corteiz 110s" and the raw edge of the denim.',false,'2026-04-29T05:24:21.433939+00:00'),
('7cabafdc-8b94-4def-a1de-eedc625a2b4f','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Casual day out','This outfit embraces a **Neutral Anchor** colour story with an accent. The White Hellstar Records Graphic T-Shirt acts as a clean, crisp base, allowing the graphic to pop. We''ve paired these with the Light Wash Wide-Leg Denim Jeans, which bring a relaxed streetwear vibe and comfort for a casual day out. The black and yellow of the Honey Black Corteiz 110s ground the look with a sporty, street-formal edge and offer a subtle but effective pop of color against the otherwise neutral tones. This combination aligns perfectly with your ''Street Formal'' style preference, balancing casual comfort with distinct streetwear elements.','To elevate this casual look, try cuffing the jeans slightly to showcase the sneakers.',false,'2026-04-30T08:09:26.467678+00:00'),
('fe9b70b3-b3d4-4dea-9f25-fdf7be179fe8','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Casual day out','This casual day out look goes for a neutral anchor colour story, combining the classic black of the Stone Island x Supreme tee with light wash denim and grey sneakers. The Stone Island x Supreme Black Cotton Tee provides that essential streetwear edge, while the Light Wash Wide Leg Denim Jeans offer a relaxed, stylish silhouette that aligns perfectly with your ''Street Formal'' preference. Finishing the outfit with the Cool Grey Jordan 4s ties in the grey tones from the denim and provides a comfortable yet fashionable streetwear shoe.','To elevate this casual look, consider adding a simple chain or a watch for a subtle touch of sophistication.',false,'2026-04-30T08:09:35.373427+00:00'),
('b4e3db0a-5051-49c5-9e54-9e8cfd7c4f68','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Casual day out','This "Street Formal" casual day out look uses a Neutral Anchor colour story of black and dark grey with a pop of yellow. The Black Corteiz Rtw tee in cotton provides a crisp, dark base, aligning with a sleek streetwear aesthetic. Washed black baggy jeans offer a relaxed yet stylish bottom, perfectly fitting the casual occasion and the user''s preference for baggy styles. The Honey Black Corteiz 110s tie the look together, their black coordinating with the top and jeans while the "Honey" yellow detail adds an unexpected stylistic flair, making the outfit feel dynamic.','Roll up the cuffs of your jeans slightly to show off the sneakers.',false,'2026-04-30T08:10:18.692256+00:00'),
('ff7601d1-2836-445b-8ff4-1c170a560b68','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Casual day out','This "Street Formal" look for your casual day out leans into a monochromatic neutral-anchor colour story. The black Gallery Dept. Washed Black Tee offers a relaxed yet stylish base, while the Washed black baggy jeans provide a comfortable, contemporary streetwear silhouette that aligns with your preferred style. The cool grey Jordan 4s tie the whole look together with their subtle tonal variation and athletic-casual vibe, making for a cohesive and effortlessly cool ensemble. The dark tones will flatter your unspecified skin tone by providing a sophisticated contrast that is universally appealing for a casual setting.','For an elevated streetwear touch, try cuffing the jeans slightly to showcase the sneakers.',false,'2026-04-30T08:10:28.755517+00:00'),
('0f73e727-3ab8-4e7d-bcbf-41926521d27b','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Casual day out','For a casual day out, I''ve curated a Street Formal look with a Neutral Anchor colour story around black. The Black Nofs Hoodie provides a sleek, monochromatic base, aligning with your preferred neutrals and offering a clean streetwear aesthetic. Paired with the Washed Black Baggy Jeans, made from sturdy denim, the outfit maintains a relaxed yet put-together vibe that''s perfect for your athletic body type. Finally, the Honey Black Corteiz 110s tie the look together with their black and yellow accents, adding a subtle pop of colour while keeping it firmly rooted in the streetwear style you favor.','To elevate this casual look, try cuffing the jeans slightly to showcase the sneakers.',false,'2026-04-30T08:10:34.353005+00:00'),
('c314bf1f-4627-4bc9-8209-96caf35c0b30','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Casual day out','This "Street Formal" outfit for a casual day out uses a Neutral Anchor colour story, combining the core neutrals of grey and black with a subtle accent. The Grey Broken Planet Zip-Up Hoodie offers a relaxed yet stylish top, perfectly aligned with the user''s streetwear preference. Paired with the Washed black baggy jeans, the outfit maintains a comfortable, contemporary streetwear vibe. The "Cool grey jordan 4s" complete the look, tying in with the grey tones of the hoodie and adding a classic, athletic touch that complements an athletic body type and the casual occasion.','Wear the hoodie unzipped with a plain black tee underneath for an additional layer of style and comfort.',false,'2026-04-30T08:10:39.821939+00:00'),
('4dfc6238-30d9-439d-afba-29ffffe48374','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Casual day out','Gallery Dept. Washed Black Tee, Washed black baggy jeans, and Honey Black Corteiz 110s work together for casual day out because the mix of tops, bottoms, and shoes feels intentional from top to bottom. The black, dark blue, blue, dark grey, black, charcoal, and black, yellow palette creates clean contrast and visual balance, which helps the outfit feel polished and easy to wear. The cotton, denim, and leather fabrics fit the tone of casual day out, balancing comfort with the right amount of structure and texture. It also aligns with your street formal style preference, so the final look feels personal and believable instead of like a random mix of separate items.','To lean into the street formal aesthetic, consider adding a simple silver chain or a minimalist cap.',false,'2026-04-30T08:10:48.032786+00:00'),
('a9d5aea7-0be2-489a-b386-834c994d0cea','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Casual day out','For your "Casual day out" and "Street Formal" style, we''re building around a Neutral Anchor colour story using white, black, and grey. The crisp White Corteiz RTW Tee in cotton provides a clean, streetwear-inspired top. Pairing it with the Washed Black Baggy Jeans in denim creates a relaxed yet stylish silhouette that aligns with your preferred aesthetic. Finally, the Cool Grey Jordan 4s in leather bring in that essential streetwear element, grounding the outfit with a classic athletic sneaker that complements the black and grey tones. This outfit embodies a polished casual look without sacrificing comfort or your street style.','For an extra touch of "Street Formal," consider adding a simple silver chain or a classic black watch.',false,'2026-04-30T23:18:33.781011+00:00'),
('c4dac541-42c4-44ad-b073-9e467081853d','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Casual day out','This outfit works for a casual day out at 15°C by embracing a Neutral Anchor colour story with shades of black, grey, and yellow for a Street Formal aesthetic. The "Gallery Dept. Washed Black Tee" and "Washed black baggy jeans" provide a relaxed yet intentional base. Adding the "Arc''teryx Black Beta LT Jacket" brings in a technical streetwear element, perfect for the cooler weather while maintaining a sleek silhouette. The "Honey Black Corteiz 110s" tie the look together with hints of black and yellow, adding a subtle pop of colour and maintaining a cohesive feel that complements the athletic body type and "Street Formal" style preference.','Layer a subtle chain or necklace under the tee for an elevated touch.',false,'2026-04-30T23:18:40.069652+00:00'),
('78d93e51-3776-4fa9-8596-04dcd7d0b881','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Casual day out','This outfit embodies your "Street Formal" style for a casual day out at 15°C. We''re building a Neutral Anchor colour story with black, grey, and cream, punctuated by subtle yellow accents. The Black Corteiz Rtw tee in cotton provides a comfortable, breathable base, while the Washed black baggy jeans offer a relaxed yet stylish streetwear foundation. Paired with Honey Black Corteiz 110s, the yellow detailing ties the look together with the dark tones. Layering the Grey Cp company zip up over the top adds warmth for the cooler weather.','For an elevated streetwear look, leave the zip-up hoodie unzipped to show off the tee, and maybe add a simple silver chain.',false,'2026-04-30T23:18:52.143749+00:00'),
('64c72ce2-911f-4293-926c-829df12ec81f','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Casual day out','This "Street Formal" outfit for a casual day out at 15°C perfectly blends comfort and style. The Monochromatic colour story, centred on black and grey, creates a sleek, cohesive look. The `Black Nofs Hoodie` provides a relaxed yet structured base, while the `Washed black baggy jeans` add a street-inspired, contemporary silhouette in a complementary dark grey denim. Paired with `Cool grey Jordan 4s`, the outfit maintains a sporty-luxe feel. Finally, the `Arc''teryx Skull cap` completes the ensemble, offering warmth and an urban edge suitable for the cool, clear weather, without overwhelming the minimalist aesthetic.','Balance the bagginess of the jeans by ensuring the hoodie has a good fit, and let the sneakers be the subtle statement piece.',false,'2026-04-30T23:19:01.297766+00:00'),
('6ffa5622-c8cd-4f86-a8f5-65553f51c90f','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Casual day out','For a casual day out at 15°C, this outfit captures a ''Street Formal'' aesthetic with a comfortable yet put-together feel. We''re going with a Neutral Anchor colour story using black and darker tones as the base, with a subtle pop of yellow. The Corteiz waffle knit Grindwear dark blue tee offers a comfortable, structured top with its knit fabric, perfect for the mild weather. It pairs seamlessly with the Washed black baggy jeans, which lean into the streetwear aspect of your style preference, while remaining classic and versatile. The Honey Black Corteiz 110s complete the look, their black and yellow tones providing a stylish anchor and a touch of individuality to the otherwise neutral palette.','Roll up the cuffs of your jeans to highlight the sneakers and add a laid-back touch.',false,'2026-04-30T23:20:42.430363+00:00'),
('5cea6f3b-6786-4b17-a6f5-5a96056286bd','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Casual day out','This outfit works with a "Neutral Anchor" colour story, using black and grey as the base. The Stone Island x Supreme Black Cotton Tee provides a clean, streetwear-aligned base. Pairing it with the Washed Black Baggy Jeans creates a relaxed, contemporary silhouette that aligns with your "Street Formal" aesthetic while keeping you comfortable in 15°C weather. The Grey Broken Planet Zip-Up Hoodie adds an extra layer for warmth and a touch of modern streetwear. Finally, the Cool Grey Jordan 4s tie the whole look together with their grey tones, perfectly complementing the outfit while offering a sporty finish that enhances the casual appeal.','For an elevated streetwear vibe, try wearing the hoodie unzipped with the tee visible.',false,'2026-04-30T23:20:50.904717+00:00'),
('9b599003-7a11-4b56-8e8e-7c6eb133c87e','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','colourful outfit','This "colourful outfit" for a 15°C clear day embraces the user''s "Street Formal" style and preference for bold colours with a complementary colour story. The Multi-color Corteiz world cup chaos Long sleeve tee is the focal point, blending streetwear aesthetics with a vibrant palette. It''s paired with the Light Wash Wide Leg Denim Jeans, providing a casual yet refined base that complements the top''s busy pattern. Finally, the Anatomy of air 110s in Red, Dark Red, Burgundy, and Coral tie the look together with a pop of complementary color, aligning with the "Street Formal" vibe and adding an athletic edge.','Roll up the sleeves of the long sleeve tee slightly to add a relaxed touch and show off any wrist accessories.',false,'2026-04-30T23:20:58.714354+00:00'),
('6bb7ab94-95b1-439a-9cfb-95f168c316e6','d37b0f1b-85f6-4b70-aebf-1f11f6d9ffad','','','Casual day out','This "Street Formal" look for a casual day out uses a Neutral Anchor colour story with a pop of muted grey. The Gallery Dept. Washed Black Tee offers that slightly oversized, vintage streetwear vibe you love, balancing the more tailored feel of the Washed black baggy jeans. The charcoal denim in the jeans keeps the outfit grounded and sophisticated. Finishing with the Cool grey Jordan 4s ties in the streetwear aesthetic with a classic, comfortable sneaker that complements the black and charcoal tones without being too stark. This combination offers a relaxed yet elevated feel, perfect for your athletic body type.','Roll up the hems of your jeans slightly to show off the Jordan 4s and add a bit of intentional nonchalance.',false,'2026-05-01T04:06:32.87888+00:00'),
('b3c3f944-aec7-4393-9844-1a5c9da2ac26','146c3b39-8c54-4f9e-95a9-daf0b435c36f','','','Casual day out','This outfit embraces your casual, sporty style with a complementary colour story. The "RH Auckland Jersey" in Navy Blue provides a strong athletic top. We''re pairing this with the "Black and White Polyester Athletic Shorts," creating a comfortable and functional base. For footwear, the "White and Black Adidas Running Shoes with Neon Accents" perfectly tie into the athletic vibe. This combination is ideal for a casual day out, offering both comfort and a cohesive sporty aesthetic.','Roll up the shorts a bit for a more relaxed look, and remember to coordinate socks with your neon accents!',false,'2026-05-01T08:10:12.997674+00:00'),
('ef223d12-3814-4b70-92da-f9b1869d25e5','146c3b39-8c54-4f9e-95a9-daf0b435c36f','','','Casual day out','For your casual day out in 15°C clear weather, I''ve put together a sporty yet comfortable outfit using an Analogous colour story with shades of blue and navy, anchored by a crisp white shoe. The Auckland Regional Talent Hub top in navy blue polyester offers a sporty vibe and good layering for the mild temperature, aligning perfectly with your sporty style preference. I''ve paired it with the Dark Wash Denim Jorts, a casual and comfortable choice in blue denim that complements the top without being too heavy or warm. Finishing the look, the White and Black Adidas Sneakers provide comfort, a clean contrast, and continue the sporty aesthetic. This combination is practical for the weather and perfectly captures your sporty, casual style.','Roll up the hems of your jorts slightly for a relaxed, modern touch.',false,'2026-05-01T08:10:23.861225+00:00'),
('5df494e5-1f4c-4372-bbdf-b381f24f6925','146c3b39-8c54-4f9e-95a9-daf0b435c36f','','','Casual day out','This casual outfit for a 15°C clear day embraces a "Neutral Anchor" colour story with a sporty and relaxed vibe, perfect for your style preference. The Baggy Grey Leisure Club shirt offers comfort and a cool, laid-back aesthetic, ensuring you stay comfortable in the mild weather. Paired with the Black Athletic Shorts, the look remains consistently sporty and allows for ease of movement. Finally, the White and Black Adidas Sneakers tie in the athletic theme while providing a clean, fresh contrast and practicality for a casual day out.','Roll up the sleeves of the shirt slightly for an even more relaxed feel.',false,'2026-05-01T08:10:32.334201+00:00'),
('227998cb-0cfc-4259-9cf1-70492dfd0d71','146c3b39-8c54-4f9e-95a9-daf0b435c36f','','','Brunch with friends','For a smart casual brunch at 15°C, I''ve gone with a Neutral Anchor colour story using beige, blue, and white. The Beige Cotton T-shirt is a comfortable and stylish base, aligning with your casual and sporty style. Paired with Dark Wash Denim Jorts, this keeps the outfit relaxed yet put-together for the occasion. The White and Black Adidas Sneakers maintain the sporty aesthetic while being clean and appropriate for brunch.','To elevate this casual look, add a classic watch or a subtle bracelet.',false,'2026-05-01T08:15:13.026234+00:00'),
('ba4855aa-f123-460d-9b7c-a9a400604926','146c3b39-8c54-4f9e-95a9-daf0b435c36f','','','Brunch with friends','For a Smart Casual brunch at 15°C, I''ve selected a Neutral Anchor colour story around beige and blue. The Beige and Navy Plaid Short-Sleeve Button-Up Shirt offers a polished yet relaxed feel, perfect for your casual and sporty style. Paired with Dark Wash Denim Jorts, the outfit maintains a comfortable and laid-back vibe while still looking put-together. The White and Black Adidas Sneakers tie in the sporty aesthetic of your style, keeping the entire look cohesive and appropriate for the casual occasion and clear weather.','Roll up the sleeves of the button-up and add a simple watch for a touch of refined casualness.',false,'2026-05-01T08:15:24.877541+00:00'),
('5c480128-9167-45b2-a286-0714bdc87f6b','146c3b39-8c54-4f9e-95a9-daf0b435c36f','','','Job interview','This job interview outfit uses a Neutral Anchor colour scheme, combining the sophisticated tones of beige with classic blue. The Beige and Navy Plaid Short-Sleeve Button-Up Shirt, made of breathable cotton, provides a smart yet comfortable top for the 15°C clear weather. Paired with the Dark Wash Denim Jorts, also in a classic blue, this creates a cohesive and slightly more relaxed take on business appropriate, aligning with your casual and sporty style preference. The White and Black Adidas Sneakers complete the look, offering a clean and modern finish that keeps the overall vibe approachable for a casual interview setting. While prioritizing your sporty style, this outfit maintains a polished appearance suitable for a business occasion.','For a slightly more polished look, consider cuffing the denim jorts neatly.',false,'2026-05-01T08:15:33.773651+00:00'),
('71f820a7-56f2-4e28-b3b7-362c6011da6d','146c3b39-8c54-4f9e-95a9-daf0b435c36f','','','Business meeting','This outfit is built around a Neutral Anchor colour story, combining beige and navy with white. For a business meeting at 15°C, the "Beige and Navy Plaid Short-Sleeve Button-Up Shirt" provides a smart yet casual top that aligns with your preferred casual and sporty style, making it appropriate for a business setting without being overly formal. We''ve paired this with the "Dark Wash Denim Jorts" to maintain a touch of casualness while still being presentable for business, as dark, clean denim is often acceptable in contemporary business casual environments. The "White and Black Adidas Sneakers" complete the look, offering a clean, sporty, and comfortable option that ties in with the neutral palette and your athletic leanings, while remaining smart enough for the occasion.','For a slightly more polished look, ensure your jorts are well-fitted and free from any rips or distressing.',false,'2026-05-01T08:15:41.572232+00:00'),
('8f83ee6a-cc7a-4113-8a50-0e39a2c3c0bb','146c3b39-8c54-4f9e-95a9-daf0b435c36f','','','Beach / Vacation','This outfit embraces a "Neutral Anchor" colour story with navy and black as the base, allowing the vibrant rust from the shorts to be the accent. The "Auckland Regional Talent Hub" navy polyester top is a sporty, casual choice perfectly suiting the user''s style preference and is breathable for a 15°C beach day. It pairs well with the "Harbour Cricket Shorts" which feature black and rust, adding a touch of sporty flair without being overly athletic. The "White and Black Adidas Running Shoes with Neon Accents" complete the look, providing comfort and a subtle pop of colour while maintaining the sporty, casual vibe of the outfit and fitting the occasion perfectly.','Roll up the shorts slightly to adjust the length for a more relaxed look.',false,'2026-05-01T08:15:48.04275+00:00'),
('e3b1dbda-bd18-4aa4-af51-01f89cd7175b','0efc7833-4b0b-406a-9bc8-4ce683341c40','','','Beach / Vacation','This outfit embraces a "Neutral Anchor" colour story around light grey, cream, and blue for a relaxed yet put-together beach-holiday vibe. A crisp White Cotton Crew Neck T-Shirt offers a clean, casual base that is perfect for warm weather. The Light Gray Wide Leg Sweatpants made of breathable polyester provide comfort and a modern, relaxed silhouette, ideal for a casual vacation setting. Paired with Louis Vuitton Monogram Denim Sneakers, this adds a touch of subtle luxury and a cool blue accent to the neutral palette. To complete the look and offer a touch of refinement that aligns with your old-money preference, the Dior Oblique Canvas Baseball Cap in grey adds a stylish and cohesive accessory.','Roll up the cuffs of the sweatpants slightly to showcase your sneakers and create a more intentional, stylish look.',false,'2026-05-02T12:27:10.608607+00:00'),
('1a1eb962-1fd1-48f2-b85e-d530e3402faa','0efc7833-4b0b-406a-9bc8-4ce683341c40','','','Casual day out','This casual day out look is built on a Neutral Anchor colour story, combining the classic Light Grey of the Essentials Fear of God Hoodie with the subdued Grey of the Wide-Leg Trousers. This pairing creates a refined yet relaxed foundation, perfectly aligned with your preference for neutrals and earth tones, as well as your casual and old-money style. The luxurious Silk fabric of the trousers elevates the comfort of the hoodie, providing a sophisticated feel suitable for a mild 12°C day. The White and Olive Green Nike Sneakers, even though worn recently, are the only option available that ties the neutral tones together and adds a sporty, effortless touch without being too stark against the grey.','For an elevated casual look, cuff the silk trousers just above the ankle to showcase your sneakers and add a touch of intentional detail.',false,'2026-05-02T12:46:56.323779+00:00'),
('a533aa85-88eb-446f-8daf-1eeef1a9dc23','0efc7833-4b0b-406a-9bc8-4ce683341c40','','','Gym / Workout','This outfit uses a "Neutral Anchor" colour story centered on navy and grey with an accent of olive green from the selected shoes. The classic Navy Cotton T-shirt offers a clean, versatile base that aligns with your preferred neutral colours and casual style. Paired with the Grey Shorts, the look remains coherent and suitable for an active occasion, while the cotton fabric ensures breathability. The White and Olive Green Nike Sneakers bring a subtle touch of colour and comfort, completing a functional yet stylish ensemble for your gym workout.','For a cohesive look, ensure your socks are either white or match the grey of your shorts or the olive green of your sneakers.',false,'2026-05-02T14:02:13.725667+00:00')
